{"about_the_game":"A legendary Space Opera? Perhaps. A silly oldschool RPG with dice instead of combat? Definitely.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCaptain Spice and his small band of misfits must embark on a thrilling adventure with their space ship, the Cool Ship, while they try to stop an evil Space Wizard from destroying the galaxy. This game has it all: A duck, dice, NPCs, a guy named Slappy, a very long discussion with a flautist, Simon freaking Tower as an evil villian. What more could you ask for?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSpice Pirates in Space: a Retro RPG does not take itself too seriously. It's a fun story that usually can get a few laughs. I made it myself and it is not a AAA game. It costs less than a beer and hopefully you enjoy it almost as much!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"New Kid on the Block","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/977380/6092fe0f0b738c2af431356c2c9584767e2f0d29.jpg"},{"name":"Chet BerkSMASHer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/977380/ade927ea0f0b0d0605ef35acdcac13a658eb7b8a.jpg"},{"name":"All You Have Left in This World","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/977380/e98b1810f2b2da4f175a8e2a3198c6cf4d7d1ea3.jpg"},{"name":"Flautist or Flutist?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/977380/d1ce066e253648e29d5e70717f5cd48069608ee3.jpg"},{"name":"A Certain Set of Skills","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/977380/dfe5e5a33fa48923d841686e279d1745b740a869.jpg"},{"name":"That Maze was too Mazy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/977380/37e247bb473011eb67b6310b526f05bc1b8822f7.jpg"},{"name":"The Final Battle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/977380/e874be536a731419ea038a9490f7f769771ffb49.jpg"},{"name":"Spicy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity